{"tid":2025584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「驚方訊息」將會在杜汶澤旗下頻道「重現」","createTime":"2020-05-20T10:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T12:10:58.000Z","uid":212884,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0278420bd36489eefa6a5b8c5a40697648fd2fb5","tid":2025584,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:43:03.000Z","msg":"近日被通訊管理局強烈批評的港台節目《頭條新聞》，節目中由藝人王喜主持、諷刺警方的「驚方訊息」環節，正是風眼所在。王喜今日（20 日）下午在 YouTube 直播，公布「驚方訊息」將會在杜汶澤旗下頻道「重現」，又成立網上收費平台「喜台」，希望在更自由的環境繼續發表創作內容。<br />\n<br />\n王喜又批評通訊局的決策無理，質疑角色「忠＿勇毅」如何侮辱警隊，認為只有警員的行為才有侮辱警隊的資格。曾任職皇家香港警察的他，又斥警察本來是市民在危難中的希望，但今日的警隊卻變成「將市民推入危難的絕望」，表示會繼續以嬉笑怒罵諷刺時弊，將警察的劣行呈現出來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%8E%8B%E5%96%9C%E7%99%BC-%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E6%BC%94%E8%AA%AA-%E9%A9%9A%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-%E8%BD%89%E6%9D%9C%E6%B1%B6%E6%BE%A4%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%93-%E8%B2%AC%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%8A%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%B0%87%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%8E%A8%E5%85%A5%E5%8D%B1%E9%9B%A3%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2596%259C%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2581%25B7%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%259D%259C%25E6%25B1%25B6%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%2581%2593-%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25BB%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259B%25A3%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=b92250e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2596%259C%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2581%25B7%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%259D%259C%25E6%25B1%25B6%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%2581%2593-%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E7%2